 pending'} / ${snapshot.selected_tone_profile?.label ?? 'Tone pending'}`}\n            />\n\n            <SummaryPanel\n              description={buildProductionCopy(snapshot)}\n              label=\"Production\"\n              title={activeStage.label}\n            />\n          </section>\n\n          {snapshot.continuity_bible != null && continuityFactGroups.length > 0 ? (\n            <section\n              aria-label=\"Continuity bible\"\n              className=\"workspace-stage-panel continuity-inspector\"\n            >\n              <div className=\"panel-heading\">\n                <div>\n                  <h3>Continuity bible</h3>\n                  <p>{snapshot.continuity_bible.summary_text}</p>\n                </div>\n                <Badge tone=\"brand\">\n                  Revision {snapshot.continuity_bible.revision_number}\n                </Badge>\n              </div>\n\n              {continuitySourceCopy != null ? (\n                <p className=\"workspace-stage-detail__note\">\n                  {continuitySourceCopy}\n                </p>\n              ) : null}\n\n              <CardGrid columns={3}>\n                {continuityFactGroups.map((group) => (\n                  <SummaryPanel\n                    key={group.category}\n                    label={group.label}\n                    title={`${group.facts.length} fact${group.facts.length === 1 ? '' : 's'}`}\n                    tone={\n                      group.category === 'voice_constraint' ||\n                      group.category === 'unresolved_thread'\n                        ? 'accent'\n                        : 'default'\n                    }\n                  >\n                    <ul className=\"continuity-inspector__list\">\n                      {group.facts.map((fact) => (\n                        <li key={fact.key}>\n                          <strong>{fact.title}</strong>\n                          <span>{fact.detail}</span>\n                        </li>\n                      ))}\n                    </ul>\n", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '1930,2025p' frontend/src/pages/session/SessionWorkspacePage.tsx\"", "exit_code": 0, "id": "item_123", "status": "completed", "type": "command_execution"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 252, "prompt_index": 56, "prompt_name": "55 \u2014 Continuity Bible and World-State Tracker", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T03:55:30-07:00"}
